snippet.title: Claws of Furry | Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
The new Rogue-like action game is here! Punch and claw your way through forty fast paced levels of pure mayhem, while honing your Ninja Cat skills, in order to rescue your Master from the evil claws of an unknown enemy.

Visit the steam page: http://store.steampowered.com/app/656580/Claws_of_Furry/

Learn more at
http://www.clawsoffurry.com/

Like us on Facebook
https://www.facebook.com/clawsoffurry/

Follow us on Instagram
https://www.instagram.com/claws_of_furry/
